OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,FNew parents in Guernsey say they are
OL,7,Ffrustrated over the island's parental
OL,8,Fleave provision, which is among the
OL,9,Fworst in the Western world.
OL,11,FUnlike Jersey and the UK, Guernsey
OL,12,Fdoes not force employers to offer paid
OL,13,Fmaternity or paternity leave. Instead,
OL,14,Fparents can receive a statutory
OL,15,Fallowance that is less than minimum
OL,16,Fwage.
