OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,F"But the reality of when you are
OL,7,Fpregnant and going on maternity leave
OL,8,Fis very different. I did rely on my
OL,9,Fsavings."
OL,11,FThe amount of maternity leave a mother
OL,12,Fcan take in Guernsey is much less than
OL,13,Fin Jersey and the UK, and as it
OL,14,Fstands, there is no legal requirement
OL,15,Ffor employers to pay for it.
OL,17,FAlso, teacher Kat Arlington found out
OL,18,Fthat if a parent has not been on the
OL,19,Fisland long enough, they are not
OL,20,Feligible for the full 26 weeks.
