OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,FShe says it means she has been forced
OL,7,Fto turn down work opportunities,
OL,8,Fexplaining: "We decided to be really
OL,9,Ftransparent with the head teacher and
OL,10,Fto let him know from the outset.
OL,12,F"But then, that's when he informed me
OL,13,Fthat the maternity leave would only be
OL,14,Fthree months, so unfortunately, we
OL,15,Fcouldn't go ahead with the position."
OL,17,FGuernsey law allows just two weeks of
OL,18,Fcompulsory paternity leave for fathers
OL,19,F- 50 weeks below Jersey and the UK -
OL,20,Fand no statutory pay.
