OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,FThere are also concerns over the
OL,7,Fisland's birth rate, which is
OL,8,Funsustainably low.
OL,10,FOver the past 10 years, it has dropped
OL,11,Fby 33% to 422 births last year.
OL,13,FITV News also understands that leave
OL,14,Fand pay security changes widely
OL,15,Fbetween professions, with people now
OL,16,Fchoosing jobs based on what parental
OL,17,Fleave is offered.
