OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,FThose differences are something Teresa
OL,7,FBott, manager of the children's
OL,8,Fnursery Bright Beginnings, says she
OL,9,Fhas heard first-hand.
OL,11,FShe says: "Having spoken to some of
OL,12,Four parents recently, I think it's not
OL,13,Fa one-size-fits-all and perhaps that's
OL,14,Fthe problem.
OL,16,F"It depends on who you work for. It
OL,17,Fdepends on the policies in your own
OL,18,Fplace of work."
