OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,FWhile Guernsey's maternity and
OL,7,Fpaternity legislation has stagnated,
OL,8,Fsome countries have made massive leaps
OL,9,Fforward.
OL,11,FIn Estonia, a parent can take up to
OL,12,Fone and a half years off at full pay.
OL,14,FArther Panov, a Family Policy Advisor
OL,15,Fat the Estonian Ministry of Social
OL,16,FAffairs, told ITV News: "During the
OL,17,Fparental leave, you are entitled to
OL,18,F100% of your income that you were
OL,19,Fearning one year before the beginning
OL,20,Fof the pregnancy.
