OL,3,CWhy Guernsey's parental leave is among
OL,4,Cthe worst in the Western world
OL,6,F"When this maternity leave ends, any
OL,7,Fparent, either mother or father, is
OL,8,Fentitled to share parental leave,
OL,9,Fwhich can last up to when a child is
OL,10,Fthree years old."
OL,12,FITV News contacted the new President
OL,13,Fof Employment and Social Security,
OL,14,FDeputy Tina Bury, on whether there are
OL,15,Fplans to change Guernsey's legislation.
OL,17,FHowever, we were told that the
OL,18,Fcommittee needs some time before it
OL,19,Fcan decide its priorities for the
OL,20,Fpolitical term.
